{
  "stem": "23498.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She used to-- that behind my back because I never knew that she used to go out with him once or twice.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he said that he will hide her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I said, I haven't got a contact with her anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But you, oh, you better don't show yourself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He hates Jews, but he likes that Jewess.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know, that was his words.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Lolek, I came about myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I haven't got where to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "My mother is looking, in the meantime, for a place for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But actually, I can't stay where I am.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Maybe it's a question of months or-- so my mother will pay how much you want her to pay.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he said to me, I can't decide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "This is my family's business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I can only say for myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I'm not against it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I'm not for it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It depends for my family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And of course, the younger brother said no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And the sister said no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after I talked to Stasek who was a-- a boyfriend, he said-- he said to me, did you have a cousin Marek?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Marek was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And next door, the flats belonged to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said that was my first cousin, Marek Frydman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, he was my best friend.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we used to have pigeons and all sorts of those [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's what do you eat-- the-- the white one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- you know, the white animal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We don't eat it, but they are very popular.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used to look after them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was very sort of like-- animals and birds and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he had-- I could see that he's got sympathy already for me because I'm the first cousin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and that Stasek said, look, you've got a radio.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
